---
const highlights = [
	"Custom software delivered end-to-end",
	"Fast execution with modern stacks",
	"Long-term support and optimization",
];
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden pb-16 pt-12 sm:pb-20 sm:pt-16 reveal" data-animate>
	<div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0">
		<div class="absolute -left-24 top-0 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-cyan-500/10 blur-[120px]"></div>
		<div class="absolute right-0 top-24 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-indigo-500/10 blur-[120px]"></div>
	</div>
	<div class="relative mx-auto flex w-full max-w-6xl flex-col gap-10 px-6 pt-6 sm:pt-10 md:flex-row md:items-center">
		<div class="max-w-2xl space-y-5 sm:space-y-6">
			<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-accent">
				Modern IT Solutions
			</p>
			<h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold leading-tight text-primary sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl">
				We deliver thoughtful IT solutions that make your operations feel effortless.
			</h1>
			<p class="text-base text-muted sm:text-lg">
				We design, build, and deliver IT solutions directly to you. From custom applications to
				reliable cloud setups, we ship polished outcomes that perform from day one.
			</p>
			<div class="flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:gap-4">
				<a
					class="btn-primary w-full sm:w-auto"
					href="#contact"
				>
					Start a project
				</a>
				<a
					class="btn-secondary w-full sm:w-auto"
					href="#services"
				>
					Explore services
				</a>
			</div>
			<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-[11px] sm:gap-3 sm:text-xs">
				{highlights.map((item) => (
					<span class="chip rounded-full px-3 py-1">{item}</span>
				))}
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="w-full max-w-md rounded-3xl border border-subtle bg-surface p-6 shadow-2xl">
			<p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-muted">Trusted Delivery</p>
			<h2 class="mt-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-primary">Built by one dedicated team.</h2>
			<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-muted">
				We handle strategy, design, and engineering in-house to deliver secure, scalable solutions
				without handoffs or delays.
			</p>
			<div class="mt-6 space-y-3 text-sm text-muted">
				<div class="flex items-center gap-3">
					<span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-[var(--accent-strong)]"></span>
					Discovery workshops and technical planning
				</div>
				<div class="flex items-center gap-3">
					<span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-[var(--accent-strong)]"></span>
					Design systems and implementation
				</div>
				<div class="flex items-center gap-3">
					<span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-[var(--accent-strong)]"></span>
					Ongoing optimization and support
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
